## Verification Checklist

- [ ] `gblockparty link` requires authentication (exits if not logged in)
- [ ] Projects are fetched from `GET /api/projects` with correct auth header
- [ ] An interactive list of projects is displayed with names and repo info
- [ ] Selecting a project creates `.gblockparty/config.json` with the correct project ID
- [ ] The `.gblockparty/` directory is created if it does not exist
- [ ] Success message shows the project name and ID
- [ ] Re-running `gblockparty link` allows selecting a different project (overwrites config)
- [ ] No projects scenario shows a helpful message
- [ ] API error scenarios are handled gracefully with informative messages
- [ ] `pnpm typecheck` passes
